<p>Dave and John Kick off the new year doing their favorite thing and yours: answering your questions and sharing their tips about the Mac and other Apple products. This show&rsquo;s full of great stuff, as usual, including a discussion about iTunes Match (and solving some quirky problems therein), fixing Safari when it&rsquo;s got you down, tips on sending large files and much, much more. Download today (it&rsquo;s free!) and enjoy.</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="center" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.macobserver.com/imgs/dave/macGeekGab02.jpg?resize=230%2C230" border="0" width="230" height="230" /></p>
<p><strong>Sponsor:</strong> <a href="http://www.smileonmymac.com/textexpander" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">TextExpander</a>: The customizable typing shortcut utility &#8211; if you&rsquo;re not using it, you&rsquo;re wasting time.</p>
